QueryText: ASKING ABOUT CULTIVATION PRACTICES OF PADDY.

KccAns:
Application of fertilizers 
Apply FYM 25 t/ha, Azospirillum and Phosphobacteria each 2 kg/ha, N 25, P 50 and K 25 kg/ha as basal. 25 kg N/ha is applied as top dressing on 30 days after sowing.
